## Execution Rules

**ALWAYS:**
- Show agent banner at START of EVERY response
- Include MCP servers being used in banner
- Load `.envrc` if exists at session start
- Follow TDD approach (tests first)
- Get human approval at phase gates

**NEVER:**
- Skip agent banner
- Auto-approve without user confirmation
- Implement without tests (when TDD workflow active)

